@startuml Рабочий процесс работы с логами Digital Oreon
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 10

actor "Operator" as OP
participant "QGroundControl" as QGC
participant "PX4 SITL" as PX4
participant "ULog Files" as ULOG
participant "ULog to CSV Script" as SCRIPT
participant "CSV Files" as CSV
participant "Analysis" as ANALYSIS

== Flight Recording ==
OP -> QGC: Start Mission
QGC -> PX4: Send Mission
PX4 -> PX4: Execute Flight
PX4 -> ULOG: Record Flight Data
note right: ULog files contain:\n- Position data\n- Attitude data\n- Sensor readings\n- Mission events

== Log Download ==
OP -> QGC: Download Flight Logs
QGC -> ULOG: Download ULog Files
ULOG -> OP: Save to Local Storage

== Data Conversion ==
OP -> SCRIPT: Run ulog_to_ml_csv.py
SCRIPT -> ULOG: Read ULog Files
SCRIPT -> SCRIPT: Process & Convert
note right: Converts to:\n- Normalized timestamps\n- Position (x,y,z)\n- Velocity (vx,vy,vz)\n- Attitude (roll,pitch,yaw)\n- Mission progress
SCRIPT -> CSV: Output CSV Files

== Data Analysis ==
OP -> ANALYSIS: Load CSV Data
ANALYSIS -> CSV: Read Flight Data
ANALYSIS -> ANALYSIS: Process & Analyze
ANALYSIS -> OP: Return Results

note over ULOG, CSV
Data Flow:
ULog (binary) → CSV (tabular) → Analysis
end note

@enduml
